From: Jasper Aorangi <3222409+spmp@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Thu, 22 Jan 2026 11:40:48 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 03/18] feat: implement rounded corner rendering for connectors

Adds support for rendering rounded corners at bend points when
connector mode is Rounded. Uses canvas arcTo() to create smooth
arcs with the configured cornerRadius (default 20px).

Note: Rough/scribbled mode doesn't support rounded corners yet
as roughjs doesn't have arcTo equivalent.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>
---
 .../src/renderer/element-renderer.ts          | 19 ++++++++++++++++++-
 1 file changed, 18 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/blocksuite/affine/gfx/connector/src/renderer/element-renderer.ts b/blocksuite/affine/gfx/connector/src/renderer/element-renderer.ts
